The paper proposes a method to improve the training of deep convolutional neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the performance of the proposed method on object recognition tasks, which is a common application of deep learning in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, and cs.NE, followed by cs.AI and cs.CL.
